Package org.goplanit.converter

Class BaseReaderImpl<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.goplanit.converter.BaseReaderImpl<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConverterEntity, ConverterReader<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NetworkReaderImpl, PlanitDemandsReader, PlanitRoutedServicesReader, PlanitZoningReader, TntpDemandsReader, TntpNetworkReader, TntpZoningReader
    public abstract class BaseReaderImpl<T>
extends Object
implements ConverterReader<T>
    Abstract base class implementation for converter readers which has a mechanism to (optionally) keep track of entities by their source id as PLANit only indexes by internal id
    Author:
    markr
